\MyProject\LolitaFramework\Core\Arr::pull
===

The Arr::pull function returns and removes a key / value pair from the array.

Example usage
---
```php

$array = ['name' => 'Desk', 'price' => 100];

$name = Arr::pull($array, 'name');

// $name: Desk

// $array: ['price' => 100]

```

Parameters
---

_array_   __$array__

_string_  __$key__

_mixed_   __$default__

Return Value
---
__mixed__
